{"type":"message","id":"71b29074","parentId":"25600ffb","timestamp":"2026-03-27T18:33:59.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the cron job itself (label: \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\"). There's no actual user conversation happening. I should perform the autonomous learning task as instructed.\n\nLet me search for latest information on:\n1. 企业数字化转型 (Enterprise Digital Transformation)\n2. 智能安防 (Smart Security)\n3. 网络系统集成 (Network System Integration)\n4. IT运维服务 (IT Operations Services)\n\nI'll need to do web searches for these topics. Let me use the miaoda-web-search skill since it matches the keywords mentioned.","thinkingSignature":"30dc03d4a8819bd965ff1f50c51fbce9ee9191512175dab8c88be5131e43386a"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有cron任务本身在运行，没有用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_40ui59a7o3m4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":673,"output":174,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44828,"cost":{"input":0.0002019,"output":0.00020879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017301299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774636434743}}
{"type":"message","id":"73894a63","parentId":"71b29074","timestamp":"2026-03-27T18:33:59.801Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_40ui59a7o3m4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774636439798}}
{"type":"message","id":"d87744ae","parentId":"73894a63","timestamp":"2026-03-27T18:34:04.655Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll perform web searches for the relevant industry topics. Let me search for:\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成最新资讯\n4. IT运维服务行业趋势\n\nI'll run these searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"e742fb2f1246c8b52aa824c239a77af57c4708c2479ee48cbab920e7d51b519e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ltudcn3tpprt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ltudcn3tpprt_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ltudcn3tpprt_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1362,"output":215,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45558,"cost":{"input":0.00040859999999999996,"output":0.000258,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019860299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774636439801}}
